<template>
    <svg 
     xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
     id="svg"
     :width="width" 
     :height="height"
     style="border: 1px solid black"
     >
        <Surface />
        <g id="objects" transform="translate(0,0)">
            <SvgNode />
        </g>
    </svg>
</template>


<script>
import Surface from './nodes/Surface'
import SvgNode from './nodes/SvgNode'
export default {
    props: {
        width: {
            type: Number,
            default: 800
        },
        height: {
            type: Number,
            default: 800
        }
    },
    components: {
        Surface,
        SvgNode
    }
}
</script>
<style scoped>

.static {
    cursor: not-allowed;

}

.draggable {
    cursor: move;
}
</style>
